<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your Kiddo Account Password</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background:
                linear-gradient(135deg, #141e30, #243b55);
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background:
                #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
            padding: 35px 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 500px;
            margin:
                auto;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform:
                    translateY(0);
            }
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight:
                600;
            color: #243b55;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .password-box {
            display: inline-block;
            background:
                linear-gradient(90deg, #00c9ff, #92fe9d);
            color: #000;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello, {{name}}</h2>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password.</p>
        <p>Please use the One-Time Password (OTP) below to continue with resetting your password:</p>
        <div class="otp-box">{{otp}}</div>
        <p>This OTP will expire shortly. Do not share it with anyone.</p>
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your account will remain secure.
        </p>
        <div class="footer">&copy; 2025 Giant. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
</body>


</html>



